# Coordination Endpoints
# Select environment: View > Command Palette > "Rest Client: Switch Environment" -> local | dev

### Create coordination entry
# @name createCoord
POST {{baseUrl}}/coordination
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "pipeline_id": "{{pipelineId}}",
  "role": "planner",
  "key": "handoff-notes",
  "value": {
    "summary": "Phase 1 planning complete",
    "next_action": "sprint-controller"
  }
}


### Get a coordination entry by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/coordination/{{coordinationId}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}


### Patch (update) a coordination entry
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/coordination/{{coordinationId}}
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "value": {
    "summary": "Updated notes",
    "next_action": "implementer"
  }
}


### Query coordination entries (filter by pipeline_id, role, key)
POST {{baseUrl}}/coordination/query
Content-Type: application/json
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

{
  "pipeline_id": "{{pipelineId}}"
}


### Archive (soft-delete) a coordination entry
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/coordination/{{coordinationId}}
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}
